{
  "stem": "3820.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He also said that he had found a place where my mother and father and my aunt would be able to be hidden by another Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And at that point, I was taken to this couple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The lady's name is Anna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't remember her husband's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were a couple in their 40s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he left me there and told me that he would come and visit me from time to time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It was the-- he did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I gather from-- from something that happened later that my parents and my aunt were hidden by someone for a little while.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But then he was-- he-- he told them to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My parents came to visit me three times through this period.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the last time was in the early winter of-- of '43, maybe-- maybe December '42, maybe January '43.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they stayed for one night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that was the last time I ever saw them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "A few weeks later, one of the partisans came and told the people that I was living with that my parents and my aunt had been caught by a German patrol and shot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My uncle Chaim died later that year.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at this point, I felt that all my contacts with my family had broken off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, 6, 7.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You learn early not to talk out of turn, not to-- you know, pretend you don't know things that are going on around you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point on the farm, the Germans were doing an almost house-to-house search.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- the-- the lady took me to a group of partisans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was with them for approximately two weeks, constantly on the move.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Things were very bad that winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
